[160.855736, "o", "\u001b[01;31m\u001b[KOverfull\u001b[m\u001b[K \\hbox (20.20493pt too wide) in paragraph at lines 5--6\r\n\\OT1/cmr/m/n/10 men. Most of the con-fi-dences were unwanted---\r\n\u001b[36m\u001b[K--\u001b[m\u001b[K\r\n\u001b[01;31m\u001b[KOverfull\u001b[m\u001b[K \\hbox (21.96426pt too wide) in paragraph at lines 7--8\r\n\\OT1/cmr/m/n/10 ni-fied un-der the name of the ``artis-tic nature''---\r\n\u001b[36m\u001b[K--\u001b[m\u001b[K\r\n\u001b[01;31m\u001b[KOverfull\u001b[m\u001b[K \\hbox (0.46426pt too wide) in paragraph at lines 13--14\r\n\\OT1/cmr/m/n/10 cooked break-fast and mut-tered Finnish in-\r\n"]
